#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:231
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "AI ICP-fit filtering keeps your volume aimed at companies that could actually buy — never spent on ones that would never buy from you."
msgstr "AI ICP-sobivuse filter hoiab su mahu suunatud ettevõtetele, kes võiksid päriselt osta — ja mitte kunagi nendele, kes sinult kunagi ei ostaks."

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:92
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "AI checks if the company website fits your profile"
msgstr "AI kontrollib, kas ettevõtte koduleht sobib sinu profiiliga"

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:377
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "AI does write your emails — but every change you make is remembered and used for the next draft."
msgstr "AI kirjutab tõesti su kirjad valmis — aga iga muudatus, mille sa teed, jäetakse meelde ja kasutatakse järgmise mustandi jaoks."

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:420
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "AI is great as <em>glue</em> between the blocks, but it's not a great block."
msgstr "AI on suurepärane <em>liim</em> klotside vahel, aga klotsina pole ta kuigi hea."

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:372
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "AI learns from how <em>you</em> write."
msgstr "AI õpib sellest, kuidas <em>sina</em> kirjutad."

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:49
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Accurate targeting, emails personalised in your own writing style, and the infrastructure to send thousands — all in one."
msgstr "Täpne sihtimine, sinu enda kirjutamisstiilis personaliseeritud kirjad ja taristu tuhandete saatmiseks — kõik ühes kohas."

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:163
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "And stale contact data destroys your domain reputation and your emails go to spam — where nobody reads them."
msgstr "Ja vananenud kontaktandmed hävitavad su domeeni maine ning su kirjad satuvad rämpsposti — kus neid keegi ei loe."

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:557
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Build a targeted list from real registry data, write something worth reading, and send it from your own inbox — all in one place."
msgstr "Ehita sihitud nimekiri päris registriandmetest, kirjuta midagi lugemisväärset ja saada see oma postkastist — kõik ühes kohas."

#: lib/colt_web/live/account/billing_live.ex:73
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Change plan"
msgstr "Muuda paketti"

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:189
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Clean data"
msgstr "Puhtad andmed"

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:182
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Clean data in. <em>Safe</em> volume out."
msgstr "Puhtad andmed sisse. <em>Turvaline</em> maht välja."

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:196
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Company data straight from the government registries, with contact details scraped recently — not a dump from years ago."
msgstr "Ettevõtteandmed otse riiklikest registritest, hiljuti kogutud kontaktandmetega — mitte aastatetagune andmehulk."

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:460
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Connect your inbox and approve the drafted sequence."
msgstr "Ühenda oma postkast ja kinnita koostatud jada."

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:97
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Contact data"
msgstr "Kontaktandmed"

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:491
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Denmark"
msgstr "Taani"

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:212
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Double-verified contacts."
msgstr "Topeltkontrollitud kontaktid."

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:214
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Every email and phone we surface actually appears on the company's own site, and we check deliverability separately — so bounces don't trash your domain."
msgstr "Iga e-post ja telefon, mille me leiame, on tegelikult ettevõtte enda lehel, ja me kontrollime kohaletoimetatavust eraldi — nii et tagasipõrked ei riku su domeeni."

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:86
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Filter companies based on government data"
msgstr "Filtreeri ettevõtteid riiklike andmete põhjal"

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:203
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Filter on what actually matters."
msgstr "Filtreeri selle järgi, mis tegelikult loeb."

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:285
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Filters narrow it down. AI tells you <em>exactly</em> who fits."
msgstr "Filtrid kitsendavad valikut. AI ütleb sulle <em>täpselt</em>, kes sobib."

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:194
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Fresh by default."
msgstr "Värske vaikimisi."

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:98
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Freshly scraped and verified"
msgstr "Värskelt kogutud ja kontrollitud"

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:238
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Fully automated sending."
msgstr "Täisautomaatne saatmine."

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:396
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "Hi Mart — saw Konvey runs last-mile for a few Tallinn 3PLs. We cut routing overhead for teams your size; worth a 15-min look?"
msgstr "Tere Mart — märkasin, et Konvey teeb mõnele Tallinna logistikafirmale viimase miili vedu. Me vähendame teiesuguste tiimide marsruutimise üldkulu; väärt 15-minutilist pilku?"

#: lib/colt_web/live/home_live.ex:430
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid "It shows in the inbox, too. People can sense the slop, and they get so much \"personalised\" AI outreach now that it all blurs together. A well-targeted, clear offer is what actually gets read."
msgstr "See paistab ka postkastis välja. Inimesed tunnevad lahja sisu ära ja saavad nüüd nii palju „personaliseeritud\" AI-pakkumisi, et kõik sulab kokku. Just hästi sihitud ja selge pakkumine on see, mida tegelikult loetakse."

